title: Kiss Man Medium Skin Tone Woman Dark Skin Tone
description: This emoji illustrates a romantic kiss between a man with a medium skin tone and a woman with a dark skin tone. It represents love, romance, and affection within a diverse heterosexual couple.

On Apple devices, the soft curvature of their faces and the gentle blush tones communicate affection and intimacy with a touch of warmth. It's a beautiful representation of love and connection, uniquely detailed by Apple's design language for expressing tender moments.
